<scriptment id="25000" point="possibility" localizationstatus="original" fictionaldate="2011-06-26" status="final">
	<part>
		<narration>Yuki looks, from the window of headquarters, at the outside crowd.</narration>
		<line id="1000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="fr">Nothing in simulation bears the importance of complexity.</line>
		<line id="2000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="fr">The number of explorable outcomes, situations, strategies; possibilities.</line>
		<line id="3000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="fr">The Range of Possibility.</line>
		<line id="4000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="fr">All criticism and improvement of simulation leads to the Range of Possibility.</line>
		<line id="5000" speaker="yuki" voicelang="fr">The Range of Possibility births wonder, discovery, depth; skill.</line>
	</part>
</scriptment>